  m_text: "Use \"A\" or Left-Arrow key to move left\r\n\"D\" or Right-Arrow key to
    move right \r\n\r\nTap \"Space\" to Jump\r\nHold \"Space\" to Jump higher , In
    level 2 you may double-jump\n\nHold \"Left-Shift\" to Sprint *Note this uses
    energy*\n\nYour aim is to collect all ingredients then pass through\nthe doors
    to the next levels\n\n\"Escape\" to access pause menu"
